    title: "MLBB Win Rate Calculator – Mobile Legends Win Rate Tool",
    shortTitle: "MLBB Win Rate",
    metaDescription: "Calculate your Mobile Legends: Bang Bang win rate. Track your MLBB statistics and see how many wins you need to reach your target win rate.",
    category: "gaming",
    icon: "Swords",
    description: "Calculate your Mobile Legends: Bang Bang (MLBB) win rate and find out how many consecutive wins you need to reach your target win rate.",
